        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="mx-auto py-20 flex w-full max-w-screen-2xl flex-col items-center justify-center gap-10 sm:pt-40"
      id="about"
    >
      <ElixorIcon class="h-16 w-40 dark:fill-white md:w-80" />
      <p
        class="max-w-xl px-10 text-center text-lg font-light tracking-tighter md:text-2xl"
      >
        Hi, we are Elixor team. Just a small team that have a big opportunity.
        We have already done a lot of projects that shows our skill.
      </p>
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-4">
        <Comments />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto pt-20 text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl lg:text-4xl font-extralight uppercase">Projects</p>
    </div>
